reviews.review:
Even though I haven't played this game long I have managed to shit my pants 10 times in one game alone. New players are put into a tense situation with a killer who can either be a challenge or a bro who lets you and your team rack up point. Even veteran players still become tense because of the whole experience of the game.
TLDR;
This is a amazing game. Buy it you won't regret it.
